if(command.startsWith("tele")) {
    try {
        String args[] = command.split(" ");
        teleportToX = Integer.parseInt(args[1]);
        teleportToY = Integer.parseInt(args[2]);
    } catch (ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException e) {
        sendMessage("Usage: ::tele <x> <y>");
    }
